beer.beer_description:
The Lumberjack IPA is the first in the new collaborative 'Canadian Series' from two of the best Canadian-Australian brewers in the country: Bad Shepherd Brewing Co and Wayward Brewing Co.

A balance of Canadian Gambrinus malts produces subtle bready and sweet flavours, paired with 'Lumberjack' hops and an addition of Spruce tips for piney aromatic notes. 

Also pairs perfectly with flannel, beards, and rough outdoorsy charm.
